verse.lines:
{lang-eng}Have you heard Him, seen Him, known Him;
Is not yours a captured heart?
Chief among ten thousand own Him;
Joyful choose the better part.{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Idols once they won me, charmed me
Lovely things that turned my face;
So it was that sin deceived me
‘Til the Lord outpoured His grace.{/lang-eng}
